basic.Peptide Name: TaARL6IP4 (ADP-ribosylation factor-like protein 6-interacting protein 4, natural AMPs; wheat, plants)
basic.Target Organism: Active against F. graminearum 5035 (IC50 22 uM), A. alternata (IC50 25 uM), F.oxysporum (IC50 >200 uM), C.higginsianum (IC50 >200 uM), and S.sclerotiorum (IC50 >200 uM).
